{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_09_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 急に段差が",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "やっとホテルに戻って来れたな\n今日は疲れただろうから、ゆっくり休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We finally made it back to the hotel.\nYou must be tired today‚ so please rest well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でもベッドに入っても\nすぐには寝付けないかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But even when I get into bed\nI might not be able to fall asleep right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "浴衣をいただけたのが嬉しくて\nまだ少しドキドキしていて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy to have received the yukata\nand my heart is still beating a little fast…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるよ\nとりあえず、フロントで鍵を受け取ってこよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel.\nFor now‚ let's go get the keys from the front desk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "なんでしょう？　……え？　今日の私のステージ\n観て下さったんですか？　ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it? …Eh? You watched my stage\nperformance today? Thank you so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依が従業員の人に話し掛けられてる……）\n（それだけいいステージだった、ってことだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rui is being approached by a hotel employee…）\n（That means the performance was that great.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.2333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "この荷物ですか？　お祭りの主催者の方から\n浴衣をプレゼントしていただいたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This bag? I received a yukata as a present\nfrom the festival organizers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4703802057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "東京に戻ったら、友人達と一緒に着てみるつもりです\nSNSに写真を載せますから、良ければ見てみて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I return to Tokyo‚ I plan to wear it with my friends.\nI'll post photos on SNS‚ so please take a look if you'd like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.0999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　一度試しに、ですか……？\nそうですね。裾の長さとか、調整した方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Just to try it on once…?\nThat's right. The hem length and other adjustments…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.566666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。この方が、浴衣の着付けを\nして下さるそうなんですが、どうしましょう……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san. This person says they'll help me\nput on the yukata‚ but what should I do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依はどうしたいんだ？\nせっかくだし、ご厚意に甘えてもいいと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would you like to do‚ Rui?\nSince it's such a kind offer‚ I think it’s okay to accept it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.466666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "では、明日の朝、お願いしてもいいでしょうか\n実は私も、早く浴衣を着てみたかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ could I ask you to help me tomorrow morning?\nActually‚ I wanted to try wearing the yukata soon too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "良かったな、瑠依\nそれにしても、着付けをしてくれる人まで現れるとは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's great‚ Rui.\nEven so‚ for someone to appear who can help with dressing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.666666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "はい、こんなに優しくしていただけるなんて……\n着付けが終わったら優とすみれに写真を送ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ to be treated so kindly…\nAfter the dressing is done‚ I'll send photos to Yu and Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.866666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "明日は、浴衣に着替えたらご連絡しますね\nあ、でも……浴衣で移動って、目立ちますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow‚ I'll contact you once I've changed into the yukata.\nOh‚ but… traveling in yukata would be conspicuous‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.5333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "明日はすぐに東京に戻る予定だしな……\n浴衣姿での移動は、多少目立つかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're planning to return to Tokyo right away tomorrow…\nTraveling in yukata might be somewhat conspicuous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも滅多にない機会だ。瑠依が嫌じゃないなら\n着て帰ってもいいんじゃないか？　俺も同行するし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's a rare opportunity. If you don't mind‚\nit might be fine to wear it home. I'll be accompanying you too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.066666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか？\nそれなら、お言葉に甘えちゃいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that okay?\nThen I'll take you up on that offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……なんだか、お祭りの前の気分です\n凄く楽しみで、ワクワクして、ドキドキして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… it feels like before the festival somehow.\nI'm so excited‚ thrilled‚ and my heart is racing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.6999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "服を着替えるだけなのに、変ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just changing clothes‚ though. It's strange‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.6999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "変じゃないよ。着る服が変われば\nものの感じ方も、世界の見え方も変わるって言うしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not strange. They say when your clothes change‚\nhow you feel and how you see the world changes too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.866666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、今日は早く休もう\n着付けがあるから、明日は寝坊出来ないしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's rest early today.\nSince there's the dressing‚ we can't oversleep tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、分かりました\nおやすみなさい、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I understand.\nGood night‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.16
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（そろそろ着替えが終わる時間かな……）\n（あ、瑠依からメッセージだ。ホテル前で合流だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder if the dressing is about finished…）\n（Oh‚ a message from Rui. Meet in front of the hotel）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.3419800000056,
          "startTime": 167.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bell-05.m4a",
          "delay": 7200.000000000017,
          "startTime": 175.3666666667
        },
        {
